title: Grateful Dead - Rocking the Cradle - Egypt 1978 (Rhino)
description:
ROCKING THE CRADLE - EGYPT 1978
Rhino 2-CD set released in HDCD 2008

Recorded at the Great Pyramid at Giza, outside Cairo, Egypt, in September 1978. The 2 discs include highlights cherry-picked from 3 nights, mostly the last night (9/16).

Sorry, I don't have the bonus DVD that came with this set.

Very goofy stuff, mastered so it sounds like it was recorded last week. It sounds best played loud through headphones.
